OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FChance of a few showers this
OL,6,Fmorning. Persistent rain will extend
OL,7,Fsoutheast this afternoon, occasionally
OL,8,Fheavy. Chance of some sleet across
OL,9,FShetland. Orkney drying up later.
OL,10,FFresh to strong north or northeasterly
OL,11,Fwinds developing later.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FRain clearing from Shetland
OL,14,Fthen a few showers this evening. The
OL,15,Frest of the night will be mainly dry
OL,16,Fwith passing isolated showers. Strong
OL,17,Fnortherly winds at first. Cold.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
