OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FThe odd light shower at first
OL,6,Fotherwise a dry with some bright or
OL,7,Fsunny intervals. Chance of rain late
OL,8,Fevening. Cold.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FEarly
OL,11,Frain on Tuesday. Otherwise sunny
OL,12,Fspells and a few showers. Becoming
OL,13,Fdrier on Thursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
